</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="direct-usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#direct-usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Direct usage</h3>
